      <p>We work with property managers across all three counties. What we offer: same-day service when we have availability (call before noon), written service documentation on every repair for your records, accurate arrival windows we actually hit, and a 90-day warranty that covers callback situations without additional charges.</p>
      <p>We understand the rental repair dynamic: a broken washer or dryer in a tenant unit needs to be addressed the same day it's reported. We don't argue about warranty versus age — we diagnose, we quote, we fix, and we document. If you manage Whirlpool appliances in multiple units and want to establish a working relationship, call us.</p>
